From the vibrant heart of Khan Market, where Cord’s store journey begins, Sanjana seamlessly blends our Lido Top in Alice Print with the Emily Skirt in Alice Olive Checks—an unforgettable statement of elegance and charm.

latestPosts.caption:
This right here is a personalised handmade cross-stitch portrait by @love.xstitch and i have to say it’s possibly the most special gift I have received in recent times !

I’ve been following their work for a while and each piece is crafted with love, detail and so much skill! Their endeavour to empower women artisans from rural India makes the initiative even more special ! So the next time you re looking out for a memorable keepsake do check them out ! 🤍🐾
